# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CODEOWNERS — required reviewers for pull requests
#
# The platform team is a required reviewer for all changes.
# Team leads are required reviewers for their own team's IAM role file.
#
# Replace @your-org/platform-team with your actual GitHub team or usernames.
# Syntax: <path pattern>   <GitHub username or team>
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Default: platform team reviews everything
*                                                    @your-org/platform-team

# IAM governance files — platform team only
terraform/environments/iam/main.tf                  @your-org/platform-team
terraform/environments/iam/variables.tf             @your-org/platform-team
terraform/environments/iam/outputs.tf               @your-org/platform-team
terraform/environments/iam/permission-sets.tf       @your-org/platform-team
terraform/environments/iam/roles.tf                 @your-org/platform-team

# Team deployer roles — team lead + platform team
# Add an entry per team following this pattern:
#   terraform/environments/iam/teams/team-<slug>.tf  @<team-lead-github-handle> @your-org/platform-team
#
# Example:
#   terraform/environments/iam/teams/team-payments.tf  @alice @your-org/platform-team
#   terraform/environments/iam/teams/team-data.tf      @bob   @your-org/platform-team

terraform/environments/iam/teams/                   @your-org/platform-team
